{"v":1,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning","title":"Red Flags From The Beginning","artist":null,"generatedAt":"2026-07-09T18:28:04.334Z","duration":314.26,"style":{"styleSentence":"A high-energy (143 BPM) pop-rock anthem driven by a driving F-major key, featuring distorted guitar swells and modern drill-style hi-hats layered over deep 808 bass pulses to create an urgent yet emotionally raw soundscape.","genre":"Pop Rock","subGenres":["Alternative Pop","Drill-Infused Pop"],"mood":"Anxious, Melancholic, Energetic, Resigned","vocalStyle":"Dynamic duet with spoken-word intros and verses alternating between intimate close-mic female leads and gritty male replies, culminating in a soaring but weary chorus.","energy":"high","language":"English","bpm":144,"bpmExact":143.55,"key":"F","mode":"major","keyConfidence":0.873,"palette":["#080808","#181818","#282828","#180808","#280808"]},"sections":[{"i":0,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::intro::0","kind":"intro","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":true,"descriptor":"Female Spoken, Close Mic"},"raw":"Intro - Female Spoken, Close Mic","text":"Fucked [Intro]","lines":1,"startT":4.64,"endT":9.6,"bars":3},{"i":1,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::spoken::1","kind":"spoken","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":true,"spoken":true,"descriptor":null},"raw":"spoken male vocals","text":"Fuckup ed up from the from the beginnbeginning\ning...\nAlways was...\nAlways was\nAlways will be...\nAlways will be[Male Spoken, Low]\nWe should’ve seen it.","lines":7,"startT":9.6,"endT":null,"bars":null},{"i":2,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::2","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":null,"group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Instrumental Break","text":"","lines":0,"startT":null,"endT":null,"bars":null},{"i":3,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::3","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":null,"group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"distorted guitar swell, drill hats, 808 pulse","text":"","lines":0,"startT":null,"endT":29.62,"bars":null},{"i":4,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::verse-1::4","kind":"verse","ordinal":1,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":"Female Lead"},"raw":"Verse 1 - Female Lead","text":"Fucked up from the jump, we were smiling through the sirens\nRed flags on the walls, but we called it perfect timi[Male Spoken]\nAlways ng\nI kept looking for the green, like a sign I could believe in\nBut the only green was money when the bills came screaming\nYou left socks on the floor like a war I couldn’t win\nUnfinished water by the sink, same fight again\nLaundry in a mountain, folding turned to blame\nOvertime kept calling and we answered it by name","lines":9,"startT":29.62,"endT":58.64,"bars":17},{"i":5,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::5","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Male Reply","text":"I was tired, you were distant\nWe were loud, never listening","lines":2,"startT":58.64,"endT":64.32,"bars":3},{"i":6,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::6","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female Lead","text":"You got secret with your phone, I got colder with my tone\nTwo people in a house still feeling alone","lines":2,"startT":64.32,"endT":73.04,"bars":5},{"i":7,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::prechorus::7","kind":"prechorus","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":"Female"},"raw":"Pre-Chorus - Female","text":"Eyes bloodshot\nNot from the rot\nBut from reading every silence like a warning shot","lines":3,"startT":73.04,"endT":79.68,"bars":4},{"i":8,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::8","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Male","text":"Stay in your lane","lines":1,"startT":79.68,"endT":82.48,"bars":2},{"i":9,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::9","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female","text":"But the lane was a graveyard\nEvery marker had our name\nEvery name had a scar\nw[Chorus - Female Lead + Male Echo]\nMaybe I as...\nshould stop","lines":6,"startT":82.48,"endT":97.28,"bars":9},{"i":10,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::10","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female Whisper","text":"AlMaybe I should drop\nLet the mountain keep the weight I never asked to carry up\nMaybe I should fall\nEcho down the hall\nLet the silence be the answer when I can’t stand up at all\nStop, drop\nWatch it all dissolve\nStop, drop\nNothing left to solve","lines":9,"startT":97.28,"endT":null,"bars":null},{"i":11,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::11","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":null,"group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Instrumental Break","text":"","lines":0,"startT":null,"endT":null,"bars":null},{"i":12,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::12","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":null,"group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"guitar riff, 808 slide, snare build","text":"","lines":0,"startT":null,"endT":111.54,"bars":null},{"i":13,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::verse-2::13","kind":"verse","ordinal":2,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":"Female Lead"},"raw":"Verse 2 - Female Lead","text":"We fought about the dishes, fought about the rent\nFought about the words we never really meant\nYou said I was dramatic, I said you never cared\nTruth is we were both just swinging at the air","lines":4,"startT":111.54,"endT":131.6,"bars":12},{"i":14,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::14","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Male Reply","text":"You checked out first","lines":1,"startT":131.6,"endT":133.2,"bars":1},{"i":15,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::15","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female Reply","text":"You locked up worse","lines":1,"startT":133.2,"endT":134.88,"bars":1},{"i":16,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::16","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Male","text":"You wanted proof","lines":1,"startT":134.88,"endT":136.48,"bars":1},{"i":17,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::17","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female","text":"You hid the hurt","lines":1,"startT":136.48,"endT":138,"bars":1},{"i":18,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::18","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"female","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Female Lead","text":"Had the green light gleaming, but it never meant go\nJust another little lie in a pretty red glow\nI should’ve seen the signs when love felt like a debt\nWhen every kiss came loaded with a thing we won’t forget","lines":4,"startT":138,"endT":150.88,"bars":8},{"i":19,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::prechorus::19","kind":"prechorus","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"both","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":"Female + Male"},"raw":"Pre-Chorus - Female + Male","text":"Eyes bloodshot\nNot from the rot\nNot from the drinks\nNot from the smoke\nBut from the mirror showing both of us the joke","lines":5,"startT":150.88,"endT":162.85,"bars":7},{"i":20,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::20","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":{"gender":"male","group":null,"spoken":null,"descriptor":null},"raw":"Male","text":"We called it passion","lines":1,"startT":162.85,"endT":164.32,"bars":1},{"i":21,"id":"red-flags-from-the-beginning::other::21","kind":"other","ordinal":null,"voice":